  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Originally `MIN_VALIDATOR_REGISTRY_CHANGE_INTERVAL` was added to prevent the validator registry from changing literally every slot when we were doing cycles. At this point, however, I'm not as sure that it's necessary, and I don't think it would break anything to remove it, and instead just have a simple condition `last_finalized_block > last_validator_set_change_slot`.",
